Hi Vijay,

A unit matrix is a matrix where all the elements are 1.  Is 

  [ 1 ]

a matrix?  Yes, it is.  (It's a 1x1 matrix.)  Are all the elements 1?
Yes, they are.  So it's a unit matrix. 

